q 0 G 1 w 50 600 m 382 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 575 Td (Saying no is a complete sentence. But here are softer options:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 560 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 545 Td (1. 'I appreciate you asking, but I can't commit to that.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 530 Td () Tj ET
