BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 500 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 485 Td (3. 'I need to check my schedule and get back to you.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 470 Td (   \(Buys time when you freeze in the moment\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 455 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 440 Td (4. 'I'm not available for that, but I hope it goes well.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 425 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 410 Td (5. 'I've already committed my time elsewhere.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 380 Td (6. 'I'm prioritizing my own needs right now.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 365 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 350 Td (7. 'No.' \(That's it. No explanation needed.\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 335 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 320 Td (8. 'I care about you AND my answer is no.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 305 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 290 Td (9. 'Let me think about what I can realistically offer.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 275 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 260 Td (10. 'I've learned that overcommitting hurts us both.') Tj ET
