BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 575 Td (I commit to my codependency recovery:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 559 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 543 Td (1. I will identify and honor my own needs daily.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 527 Td (2. I will practice saying no without guilt.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 511 Td (3. I will not take responsibility for others' feelings.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 495 Td (4. I will maintain boundaries even when uncomfortable.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 479 Td (5. I will not try to fix, control, or rescue others.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 463 Td (6. I will build an identity separate from my relationships.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 447 Td (7. I will seek support \(therapy, CoDA meetings, friends\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 431 Td (8. I will be patient and compassionate with myself.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 415 Td (9. I will celebrate small victories.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 399 Td (10. I choose ME without apology.) Tj ET
